metadata.name: Real Imaginary | Big Bang
metadata.description:
Come bend spacetime reality with quantum imaginary in the Real Imaginary Verse.

Real Imaginary Warping is an edition of artifacts living on the Ethereum blockchain from my personal exploration of the intersection of Artificial Intelligence and the behavior of matter and energy in the Real Imaginary Verse.

Each item has been carefully curated and programmatically generated from a rich set of mathematical and visual attributes mixed with custom diffusion generative models to highlight the magic of our worlds.

This collection is part of an ever growing collectable, tradeable and playable Real Imaginary NFT tokens family.

“We are what we think, all that we are arises with our thoughts, with our thoughts we make the world.” – Gautama Buddha

Discover more at http://realimaginary.eth.li
